<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Architecture Picture of Cloud Native of JD Cloud</strong></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;">In the "universal JD Cloud Onboarding" tide of the current era, more and more applications have been directly created and deployed on cloud, and the cloud native technology has become an important driving force for the enterprise intellectualization and digital transformation reforms. In the future, JD Cloud will continually increase its input in the cloud native technology to persistently update and innovate its products and services; and hopes to deeply integrate cloud native computing and ERP based on its practices of cloud native technology business in the past years and its independently researched and developed solutions for cloud native services, to empower enterprises through the cloud native technology, to help enterprises with digital transformation, and to create higher commercial value for enterprise development.</p>
